test_all_one_range:
assert [27, 29, 31, 33] == [1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1]
  At index 0 diff: 27 != 1
  Right contains 2 more items, first extra item: 1
  Full diff:
  - [1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 1]
  + [27, 29, 31, 33]
test_even_range:
assert [27, 29, 31, 33] == []
  Left contains 4 more items, first extra item: 27
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [27, 29, 31, 33]
